show.description:
Marriage, scandal, and secrets — a shocking twist turns a perfect celebration into chaos! As lavish wedding plans unfold, old rivalries resurface and a forgotten beggar makes a dramatic return.
The game is about to change… get ready for a wild, unpredictable ride!
